{
  "id": "ielts7_test2_s1",
  "title": "Cambridge IELTS 7 Test 2 Section 1",
  "audio": "ielts7_test2_s1.mp3",
  "parts": [
    {
      "name": "Section 1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "start": 0.0,
          "end": 4.94,
          "text": "MAN: Oh hello I'd like to ask about insurance for my car."
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "start": 4.94,
          "end": 9.48,
          "text": "WOMAN: Yes, of course. I'll just take a few details. What's your name?"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "start": 9.48,
          "end": 10.32,
          "text": "MAN: Patrick Jones . Example"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "start": 10.54,
          "end": 13.26,
          "text": "WOMAN: And your address?"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "start": 13.26,
          "end": 13.98,
          "text": "MAN: It's 27 Bank Road ."
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "start": 18.2,
          "end": 22.7,
          "text": "WOMAN: 27 Bank Road. Is that in Greendale?"
        },
        {
          "id": 7,
          "start": 26.42,
          "end": 28.92,
          "text": "WOMAN: And what's your daytime phone number?"
        },
        {
          "id": 8,
          "start": 28.92,
          "end": 32.12,
          "text": "MAN: My work number is 730453."
        },
        {
          "id": 9,
          "start": 42.84,
          "end": 47.96,
          "text": "WOMAN: And could I ask what your occupation is?"
        },
        {
          "id": 10,
          "start": 47.96,
          "end": 76.96,
          "text": "WOMAN: OK now a few details about your car What size is the engine?"
        },
        {
          "id": 11,
          "start": 76.96,
          "end": 77.66,
          "text": "MAN: It's 1200 ccs."
        },
        {
          "id": 12,
          "start": 79.02,
          "end": 82.94,
          "text": "WOMAN: Thank you and the make and model?"
        },
        {
          "id": 13,
          "start": 82.94,
          "end": 85.24,
          "text": "MAN: It's a Hewton Sable."
        },
        {
          "id": 14,
          "start": 85.24,
          "end": 97.16,
          "text": "WOMAN: Could you spell the model name please?"
        },
        {
          "id": 15,
          "start": 100.16,
          "end": 101.34,
          "text": "MAN: Yes S-A-B-L-E ."
        },
        {
          "id": 16,
          "start": 101.34,
          "end": 105.22,
          "text": "WOMAN: Ah yes thanks. And when was it made?"
        },
        {
          "id": 17,
          "start": 105.22,
          "end": 114.12,
          "text": "WOMAN: Lovely right I presume you've had a previous insurer?"
        },
        {
          "id": 18,
          "start": 117.26,
          "end": 122.7,
          "text": "WOMAN: Right we need to know the name of the company."
        },
        {
          "id": 19,
          "start": 122.7,
          "end": 124.64,
          "text": "MAN: Yes it was Northern Star ."
        },
        {
          "id": 20,
          "start": 126.16,
          "end": 142.68,
          "text": "WOMAN: Thank you, and have you made any insurance claims in the last five years?"
        },
        {
          "id": 21,
          "start": 145.7,
          "end": 148.2,
          "text": "MAN: Yes one in 1999."
        },
        {
          "id": 22,
          "start": 152.06,
          "end": 155.74,
          "text": "WOMAN: And what was the problem?"
        },
        {
          "id": 23,
          "start": 155.74,
          "end": 159.74,
          "text": "MAN: It was stolen but"
        },
        {
          "id": 24,
          "start": 160.56,
          "end": 167.02,
          "text": "WOMAN: That's line, Mr Jones that's all we need to know at the moment"
        },
        {
          "id": 25,
          "start": 167.4,
          "end": 173.86,
          "text": "WOMAN: And will there be any other named drivers?"
        },
        {
          "id": 26,
          "start": 181.22,
          "end": 182.26,
          "text": "MAN: Just the one"
        },
        {
          "id": 27,
          "start": 184.84,
          "end": 187.48,
          "text": "WOMAN: And his name?"
        },
        {
          "id": 28,
          "start": 187.58,
          "end": 188.94,
          "text": "MAN: Simon Paynter."
        },
        {
          "id": 29,
          "start": 189.38,
          "end": 192.96,
          "text": "WOMAN: Could you spell the surname please?"
        },
        {
          "id": 30,
          "start": 192.96,
          "end": 194.1,
          "text": "MAN: P-A-Y-N-T-E-R ."
        },
        {
          "id": 31,
          "start": 196.86,
          "end": 207.06,
          "text": "WOMAN: OK thank you And what relationship is he to you?"
        },
        {
          "id": 32,
          "start": 207.98,
          "end": 209.48,
          "text": "MAN: He's my brother-in-law ."
        },
        {
          "id": 33,
          "start": 217.28,
          "end": 224.36,
          "text": "WOMAN: And what will you or Mr Paynter be using the car for?"
        },
        {
          "id": 34,
          "start": 224.36,
          "end": 227.78,
          "text": "MAN: Well mainly for social use"
        },
        {
          "id": 35,
          "start": 227.78,
          "end": 235.24,
          "text": "WOMAN: Social use (murmuring). Will you be using it to travel to work ?"
        },
        {
          "id": 36,
          "start": 235.24,
          "end": 236.86,
          "text": "MAN: Yes sometimes."
        },
        {
          "id": 37,
          "start": 236.86,
          "end": 237.28,
          "text": "WOMAN: Anything else?"
        },
        {
          "id": 38,
          "start": 237.28,
          "end": 237.76,
          "text": "MAN: No. That's it"
        },
        {
          "id": 39,
          "start": 237.76,
          "end": 245.44,
          "text": "WOMAN: And finally when would you like to start the insurance?"
        },
        {
          "id": 40,
          "start": 245.44,
          "end": 248.8,
          "text": "MAN: I'll need it from the 31st of January."
        },
        {
          "id": 41,
          "start": 273.28,
          "end": 291.7,
          "text": "WOMAN: Right Mr Jones I'm getting a couple of quotes coming up on the computer now and the best bet looks like being with a company called Red Flag ."
        },
        {
          "id": 42,
          "start": 299.78,
          "end": 304.34,
          "text": "WOMAN: And that comes out at $ 450 per year"
        },
        {
          "id": 43,
          "start": 309.72,
          "end": 320.08,
          "text": "MAN: Well that seems OK it's quite a bit lower than I've been paying up to now"
        },
        {
          "id": 44,
          "start": 330.36,
          "end": 334.86,
          "text": "WOMAN: Great so would you like me to go ahead with that?"
        },
        {
          "id": 45,
          "start": 334.86,
          "end": 336.18,
          "text": "MAN: Sure why not?"
        },
        {
          "id": 46,
          "start": 346.5,
          "end": 348.78,
          "text": "WOMAN: How would you like to pay?"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}